metadata.name: Around The House #1
metadata.description:
The original version of „Around The House“ came out in 2006 and really was the start of my music career. This track has a special place in my heart and you can still hear it in my DJ sets from time to time.

It only makes sense to release this completely reproduced, mixed and remastered version as
my GENESIS music NFT exclusively on  Sound.xyz „The circle is now complete“ Darth Vader would say.

As a special bonus the Golden Egg winner gets to pick a name for a song on my 3rd album, which will come out later this year. Please get in touch with me via Twitter. I reserve the right to change the name if it’s racist or offensive.

Written & produced by Tensnake
